 <i>boss! Humph!</i>

00:03:13.271 --> 00:03:15.102 position:5% line:5% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>What's going on out</i>
 <i>here?</i>

00:03:16.767 --> 00:03:19.764 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>Oh, Captain Komachi. These</i>
 <i>guys just showed up begging to</i>
 <i>enlist.</i>

00:03:20.263 --> 00:03:21.894 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, volunteers, eh?

00:03:21.928 --> 00:03:23.160 position:5% line:89% align:start
(SHEILA) <i>Uh, excuse me?</i>

00:03:23.193 --> 00:03:24.092 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:03:25.091 --> 00:03:27.754 position:5% line:83% align:start
Am I too early for the next
interviews? [gasp]

00:03:27.787 --> 00:03:29.785 position:33% line:89% align:start
Huh? [gasp]

00:03:29.818 --> 00:03:31.583 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>(ALEX) Sheila! You're here?!</i>

00:03:33.613 --> 00:03:34.979 position:5% line:77% align:start
(MARCOS) <i>Holy crap, it's you!...</i>
 <i>Aw, come here, let me pinch</i>
 <i>you, see if you're real... </i>

