05 EXCEPTIONAL TWO

00:05:31.243 --> 00:05:37.035 position:7% line:71% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>Preying mostly on </i>
 <i>cockroaches, the huntsman spider</i>
 <i>has thrived and spread across</i>
 <i>the globe. </i>

00:05:38.767 --> 00:05:44.559 position:13% line:71% align:start
 <i>Fine hairs on its body can</i>
 <i>detect subtle movements,</i>
 <i>allowing it to precisely</i>
 <i>locate its prey.</i>

00:05:45.592 --> 00:05:46.891 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:05:46.924 --> 00:05:48.555 position:21% line:89% align:start
[grunts and punches]

00:05:48.589 --> 00:05:50.753 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>It impales and tears...</i>

00:05:53.150 --> 00:05:54.582 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>...then devours</i>

00:05:54.848 --> 00:05:57.046 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grunts and yells]

00:05:59.642 --> 00:06:04.737 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>It remains ready at all times, </i>
 <i>when feeding or at rest, to</i>
 <i>unleash a ferocious attack on</i>
 <i>anything that approaches. </i>

00:06:06.202 --> 00:06:08.765 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>All I wanted was for her to be </i>
 <i>happy.</i>

00:06:08.798 --> 00:06:11.761 position:21% line:89% align:start
(SHEILA) [giggling]

00:06:11.794 --> 00:06:16.422 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>But then money got in the way, </i>
 <i>And I lost that smiling face</i>
 <i>forever!  </i>

00:06:19.719 --> 00:06:23.148 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:06:23.182 --> 00:06:24.679 position:10% line:83% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>Though a fierce</i>
 <i>hunter,</i>

00:06:27.043 --> 00:06:30.739 position:16% line:71% align:start
 <i>the huntsman spider has</i>
 <i>imited stamina and must recover</i>
 <i>its strength before ambushing</i>
 <i>its next victim. </i>

00:06:33.036 --> 00:06:34.035 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:06:38.863 --> 00:06:44.856 position:10% line:83% align:start
Uh... Captain! Guys, I-...
thanks for the help.

00:06:46.521 --> 00:06:53.979 position:10% line:71% align:start
 <i>We can't risk destroying the</i>
 <i>virus samples living inside the</i>
 <i>terraformars. We need to capture</i>
 <i>as many of them as we can...</i>

00:06:54.012 --> 00:06:54.878 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>alive.</i>

00:06:54.911 --> 00:06:55.843 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:58.939 --> 00:06:59.938 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Marcos!</i>

00:07:02.102 --> 00:07:07.096 position:5% line:71% align:start
See that these roaches are left
a twisted pile of antennae.
We'll collect the ones still
hissing afterwards.

00:07:07.130 --> 00:07:08.328 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yes sir!

00:07:19.715 --> 00:07:22.811 position:13% line:83% align:start
Just try and run, filthy
bastards.

00:07:39.026 --> 00:07:40.025 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:07:45.884 --> 00:07:47.016 position:16% line:89% align:start
[grunts and struggling]

00:07:47.049 --> 00:07:47.982 position:33% line:89% align:start
[head-butt]

00:07:55.074 --> 00:07:59.435 position:5% line:77% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>The captain of the </i>
 <i>Bugs 2 mission was Donatello </i>
 <i>K. Davis... </i>

00:08:00.533 --> 00:08:04.895 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>His post-Bugs Procedure alter</i>
 <i>ego was: Paraponera clavata,</i>

00:08:04.928 --> 00:08:08.891 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>a killer ant capable of lifting</i>
 <i>almost one hundred times its</i>
 <i>own weight. </i>

00:08:10.921 --> 00:08:14.383 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>Scientists thought they'd played</i>
 <i>a clever trick on Mother</i>
 <i>Nature.</i>

00:08:14.417 --> 00:08:18.612 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>Genetic transmission of</i>
 <i>these powers was supposed to</i>
 <i>be impossible. </i>

00:08:20.443 --> 00:08:23.906 position:5% line:83% align:start
But then, turns out, Mother
Nature wanted to play along.

00:08:24.338 --> 00:08:27.569 position:5% line:83% align:start
His unique abilities... were
passed down.

00:08:28.434 --> 00:08:30.731 position:5% line:83% align:start
Extraordinary. Passed down to
whom?

00:08:32.629 --> 00:08:37.390 position:13% line:83% align:start
The leader of the Japan/U.S.
Squad 2... Michelle K. Davis.

00:08:38.589 --> 00:08:39.588 position:24% line:89% align:start
The captain's...?

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:47.212 position:7% line:71% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>Her unique powers </i>
 <i>are twofold... There's the</i>
 <i>ability she inherited from her</i>
 <i>father...</i>

00:08:49.010 --> 00:08:54.570 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>One... Two... Three... Four... </i>

00:08:58.865 --> 00:09:01.362 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>namely, the strength</i>
 <i>of the Paraponera.</i>

00:09:10.851 --> 00:09:17.843 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>Then there's the ability she </i>
 <i>gained from the Mosaic Organ</i>
 <i>procedure... also an insect</i>
 <i>type. </i>

00:09:22.637 --> 00:09:24.168 position:5% line:89% align:start
Woah...

00:09:28.763 --> 00:09:31.327 position:10% line:5% align:start
 <i>What kind of bug does that?</i>

00:09:33.624 --> 00:09:38.651 position:10% line:71% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>In the twentieth </i>
 <i>century, scientists in Malaysia</i>
 <i>discovered an ant with a bizarre</i>
 <i>form of defense...  </i>

00:09:40.949 --> 00:09:43.679 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>It commited suicide by </i>
 <i>explosion.</i>

00:09:48.474 --> 00:09:49.872 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:56.963 --> 00:10:04.421 position:10% line:89% align:start
[grunts and heavy breathing]

00:10:12.245 --> 00:10:15.275 position:5% line:83% align:start
Lame... these guys die way too
fast.

00:10:15.774 --> 00:10:19.236 position:7% line:83% align:start
(NARRATOR) <i>A rare species, it </i>
 <i>was nicknamed the blast ant.</i>

00:10:21.767 --> 00:10:24.631 position:5% line:5% align:start
(SHICHISEI) <i>These abilities can</i>
 <i>be passed on.</i>

00:10:25.596 --> 00:10:30.824 position:27% line:5% align:start
 <i>When I observed</i>
 <i>another youth's skills during</i>
 <i>his training, that's when I</i>
 <i>was certain of it. </i>

00:10:31.723 --> 00:10:36.150 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>These two are our greatest </i>
 <i>strength... and our best hope...</i>

00:10:37.682 --> 00:10:38.680 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:10:39.679 --> 00:10:43.108 position:5% line:83% align:start
Michelle K. Davis and that kid
Akari Hizamaru.

00:10:43.409 --> 00:10:44.508 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:44.541 --> 00:10:46.338 position:10% line:89% align:start
Is he there now?... On Mars?

00:10:48.403 --> 00:10:50.300 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(</i> SHICHISEI) <i>I'm starting to</i>
 <i>think there's a lot more </i>
 <i>you're not telling me.</i>

00:10:51.333 --> 00:10:56.394 position:7% line:77% align:start
Actually, on second thought,
there's something I have to tell
you first...

00:10:56.860 --> 00:11:00.322 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>We needed a strong military</i>
 <i>presence on Mars.</i>

00:11:00.722 --> 00:11:08.445 position:10% line:71% align:start
 <i>We needed all the top-ranked</i>
 <i>Japanese officers we could</i>
 <i>get... Because if something were</i>
 <i>to happen up there...</i>

00:11:10.377 --> 00:11:13.207 position:5% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Alex, stand guard on top</i>
 <i>of the escape vehicle.</i>

00:11:13.606 --> 00:11:15.204 position:30% line:89% align:start
No problem, you got it.

00:11:16.603 --> 00:11:20.032 position:10% line:83% align:start
As for these three... they're
all mine.

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.677 position:27% line:5% align:start
 <i>It's strange... </i>

00:11:41.307 --> 00:11:47.999 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>When these spontaneous mutations</i>
 <i>strike... emotions of rage and</i>
 <i>terror possess me... My non-</i>
 <i>humanness breaks through...</i>

00:11:49.497 --> 00:11:50.663 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>But with the serum...</i>

00:11:55.058 --> 00:12:04.979 position:13% line:89% align:start
[deep breaths in and out]

00:12:06.111 --> 00:12:14.101 position:5% line:71% align:start
 <i>...everything becomes clear and </i>
 <i>the world comes into focus. It's</i>
 <i>like emerging from a</i>
 <i>chrysalis... I have no fear! </i>

00:12:23.691 --> 00:12:27.120 position:5% line:83% align:start
That was for all the people who
never made it off that ship.

00:12:31.282 --> 00:12:32.281 position:33% line:89% align:start
And <i>this</i> ...

00:12:35.477 --> 00:12:38.440 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>is for pissing of Michelle... </i>
 <i>with that rank breath of yours!</i>

00:12:44.599 --> 00:12:48.595 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>But I'm not gonna kill you and </i>
 <i>there's a reason why...</i>

00:12:52.590 --> 00:12:53.589 position:24% line:5% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Mars huh?</i>

00:13:20.557 --> 00:13:21.888 position:21% line:89% align:start
You'll catch a cold.

00:13:24.220 --> 00:13:26.982 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SAKURATO) <i>Can I-... can I see</i>
 <i>that doll?</i>

00:13:27.015 --> 00:13:28.215 position:19% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Oh, uh, sure.</i>

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:32.376 position:24% line:89% align:start
Awww, it's fallin' apart.

00:13:32.677 --> 00:13:34.541 position:5% line:89% align:start
Shouldn't you be at home?

00:13:35.140 --> 00:13:37.204 position:24% line:89% align:start
This hospital <i>is</i> my home.

00:13:37.537 --> 00:13:39.035 position:41% line:89% align:start
My name's Sakarato.

00:13:40.100 --> 00:13:42.864 position:13% line:89% align:start
Sakarato Harukaze... I'm ten.

00:13:43.330 --> 00:13:45.528 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'm Akari Hizamaru, I'm twenty.</i>

00:13:47.193 --> 00:13:50.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
Woah, Akari... that's a cool
name, I like it!

00:13:52.586 --> 00:13:53.851 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yours is cool too.

00:13:54.350 --> 00:13:55.516 position:69% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:13:56.582 --> 00:13:59.844 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Uh...so... why are you in the</i>
 <i>hospital Sakurato?</i>

00:14:04.339 --> 00:14:10.166 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>Simple reason. No one in Japan </i>
 <i>was able to fix me, so I had</i>
 <i>to move here.</i>

00:14:10.964 --> 00:14:12.129 position:33% line:89% align:start
uh... [gasp]

00:14:16.159 --> 00:14:17.157 position:47% line:89% align:start
(SAKURATO) <i>Akari?</i>

00:14:18.556 --> 00:14:21.286 position:5% line:83% align:start
Sorry, I've got be going. Thanks
for this!

00:14:21.918 --> 00:14:22.917 position:44% line:89% align:start
uh?

00:14:23.483 --> 00:14:24.482 position:21% line:89% align:start
What about... this?

00:14:25.481 --> 00:14:25.515 position:13% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Catch you later, </i>
 <i>Sakarato!</i>

00:14:26.479 --> 00:14:27.478 position:21% line:89% align:start
[disappointed grunt]

00:14:57.243 --> 00:14:58.442 position:16% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>That's one down.</i>

00:14:59.141 --> 00:15:00.140 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who's next?

00:15:02.504 --> 00:15:03.503 position:35% line:5% align:start
 <i>I see it.</i>

00:15:13.890 --> 00:15:15.255 position:5% line:5% align:start
(SAKURATO) <i>I know what's wrong, </i>
 <i>Akari.</i>

00:15:15.921 --> 00:15:18.452 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>You're starting to get nervous </i>
 <i>about the mission.</i>

00:15:19.950 --> 00:15:24.811 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah right. Guess again, kiddo.
I couldn't be more ready!

00:15:24.844 --> 00:15:27.075 position:5% line:5% align:start
[giggle] Alright, if you say so!

00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:29.372 position:10% line:83% align:start
But, aren't you forgettin'
somethin'?

00:15:29.405 --> 00:15:30.404 position:33% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>huh?</i>

00:15:36.131 --> 00:15:37.895 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Hey... you fixed it!</i>

00:15:39.428 --> 00:15:41.891 position:5% line:77% align:start
(SAKURATO) <i>I'm good at stuff</i>
 <i>like that. Is it from your</i>
 <i>girlfriend?</i>

00:15:42.790 --> 00:15:44.820 position:13% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Uh, something like</i>
 <i>that.</i>

00:15:44.853 --> 00:15:47.217 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SAKURATO) Knew it! Is she gonna
come see you off?

00:15:50.248 --> 00:15:52.878 position:10% line:83% align:start
No, she's waiting for me back
in Japan.

00:15:53.511 --> 00:15:54.875 position:35% line:89% align:start
(SAKURATO) <i>Oh, I see.</i>

00:15:56.307 --> 00:16:00.369 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'm kinda jealous, because I
probably won't ever get to see
you again.

00:16:01.301 --> 00:16:07.361 position:7% line:77% align:start
All I can do... is hope that
somebody will be able to fix me
too... if that's possible.

00:16:09.358 --> 00:16:11.189 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(MICHELL) So, you met one of the</i>
 <i>patients.</i>

00:16:15.185 --> 00:16:19.180 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>I know this sounds harsh, but </i>
 <i>you really shouldn't get their</i>
 <i>hopes up.</i>

00:16:23.075 --> 00:16:24.074 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:16:25.007 --> 00:16:26.504 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's gonna get better. You're
gonna be fine.

00:16:26.537 --> 00:16:27.670 position:83% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:29.235 --> 00:16:32.065 position:5% line:77% align:start
That's why we're going to Mars,
to find things, organisms Earth
doesn't have.

00:16:32.099 --> 00:16:34.329 position:5% line:83% align:start
We're gonna find a cure for what
you've got!

00:16:35.927 --> 00:16:36.926 position:38% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:16:38.458 --> 00:16:41.355 position:5% line:77% align:start
So, Sakurato, what's the first
thing you want to do when you're
all better?

00:16:43.186 --> 00:16:44.850 position:30% line:89% align:start
I want... french fries!

00:16:44.883 --> 00:16:45.649 position:30% line:89% align:start
Lot's of 'em!

00:16:47.114 --> 00:16:49.877 position:7% line:77% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Okay! You got it! </i>
 <i>Biggest size they have! What</i>
 <i>else?</i>

00:16:49.911 --> 00:16:50.776 position:41% line:89% align:start
mmm...

00:16:51.742 --> 00:16:53.307 position:5% line:83% align:start
Karate lessons! I want to be a
fighter too!

00:16:53.341 --> 00:16:55.971 position:5% line:83% align:start
